            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the linguine for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite, then drain it, reserving a cup of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
