    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir through your<strong> crème fraîche</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained linguine</strong> with a splash of the<strong> starchy pasta water </strong>and<strong> </strong>the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy chicken linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
